    "description": "<div style='text-align:Left;'><div><div><p><span>The current version supersedes the </span><a target='_blank' href='https://doi.org/10.7916/5f2h-h527' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span><u>GRID3 COD - Health Areas v7.0</u></span></a><span>. The following changes were made:</span></p><ul><li><span>Added data for the provinces of Bas-Uele, Haut-Uele, Kwango, and Nord-Kivu.</span></li><li><span>The data for Tanganyika was updated.</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>Download province level data:</span></p><ul><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/fse0-9c79/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Bas-Uele</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/r7ef-hy18/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Equateur</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/zrrd-1x23/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Haut-Katanga</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/rbxn-hn05/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Haut-Lomami</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/vtta-0c25/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Haut-Uele</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/j498-fa85/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Ituri</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/4j1r-h346/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Kasa\u00ef</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/5011-h134/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Kasa\u00ef-Central</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/xjzj-ad35/download' rel='